title.rendered: DASH OFFROAD Y62 Patrol Satin Predator Evolution Front Bar for S5

content.rendered:
Dash Offroad Y62 Patrol Satin Predator Evolution Front Bar for S5

This is bar is different to previous versions of the Predator bar and has been developed exclusively for the series 5 Y62 Patrol from the ground up. It will allow all factory sensors and headlight washers and has been built around the radar so no relocation is necessary.

All brackets and winch cradle has been made from steel whereas the 3 piece facia is made from aluminium to make it one of the lightest bars available for this vehicle.

Note product comes with both accessory bar PLUS integrated light bar surround.

You will need to order the STEALTH 52″ Light Bar also if you would like this option and also fog lights will need to be added too.

2022 Ti Models
With the release of the new 2022 Y62 Patrol, the front grill has changed for the Ti variant (TiL remain unchanged).
The current model now has a grill that protrudes further than the 2021 TI S5. Our new Predator Evolution Bar has the centre facia modified to suit the new 2022 TI grill.
